summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fifteenth Avenue West from the south margin of Ruffner Street to Thorndyke Avenue et al in the City of Seattle, by planking under Ordinance No. 24682, creating Local Improvement District No. 2374 prescribing the rate f interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
